name: Space Delivery EXPRESS
description:
Endless space-runner.

You have been given a package that you must deliver as soon as possible! Enter your spaceship and put the pedal to the metal and avoid the asteroids!

This game was made for a Game Jam, a final project in a Unity 3D C# programming course at University of Akureyri.

Credits:

  • Music: Space Boss Battle Theme by Matthew Pablo, www.opengameart.org/users/matthewpablo
  • Spaceship by www.bevouliin.com
  • Asteroids (rocks) by Wenrexa on OpenGameArt.org
  • Space background by Screaming Brain Studios on OpenGameArt.org
